trackCensoredName: Music for Coping with Panic Attack and Anxiety
trackName: Music for Coping with Panic Attack and Anxiety
description:
Dealing with anxiety and small panic attacks every day can be tolling on your mind, body and spirit. This is why we created Music for Coping with Panic Attack, an app that will help you deal with the stress that generates these unpleasant symptoms. Within it, you will find all that is needed in order to carry out many types of meditation for anxiety disorders.

Our app includes 10 beautiful tracks, each one of which is perfect for deep meditation techniques or guided relaxation. Try listening to them! The first half is completely free, while the others can be enjoyed within the premium version of our app:

01. Soothing
02. Healing
03. Meditate
04. Chakras
05. Reduce Anxiety
06. Relief
07. Comfort
08. Ease your Mind
09. Eternal Sunshine
10. In the Sky

Are these songs not enough to relax you? How about listening to some beautiful sounds of nature in the background? We added these in the app, try playing them and choose your favorite. Finally, don't forget to make use of the timer feature, specifically created to measure how long each mindfulness meditation session should last for. Let your body energy flow back into you and let it help you dealing with anxiety.

We hope our app can aid you in searching for the peace and serenity which you truly deserve. May it be of solace during your darkest moments. If you love our music, don't forget to let us know by leaving a positive review on the store!
